objects.title: What's A CYOA?
objects.text:
A CYOA (Choose Your Own Adventure) is an interactive, text-based game where the player is immersed in a story or world and makes decisions that shape how the story unfolds.
In a CYOA, you’re presented with a scenario or world crafted by the creator. As you progress, you face various choices—from moral dilemmas to strategic decisions—and those choices determine your character’s actions, fate, and the overall direction of the story. It’s a great way for players to dive into their imagination, experiencing stories that they shape themselves through the choices they make.

objects.title: CYOA Style:
objects.text: I mainly do Original works of Supernatural settings, with rich world building, Often being Power Fantasy.

objects.title: The Marked One
objects.text:
Synopsis:

Welcome to a world veiled in secrecy, where the supernatural lurks in the shadows beyond the sight of ordinary humans. Every half century, Reality, as a defense mechanism, marks certain human souls, revealing the hidden truths behind the veil and arming them with extraordinary gifts to protect the equilibrium. As the latest Marked One, you stand at the threshold of your destiny, tasked with the monumental responsibility of carving out your path within this extraordinary realm, teeming with otherworldly challenges and formidable adversaries. Will you fulfill these responsibilities, or indulge in your desires?

Genre:

Supernatural masquerade set in Modern world

Status:

Completed (V3.5) Release Date: 18 October 2024

objects.title: Ruined Reality
objects.text:
Synopsis:

Welcome to a world amidst the crossfire of two ancient eldritch gods. Entities of flesh and the mind are locked in a fierce struggle, each seeking to corrupt humanity to their side. Their immense powers, when unleashed simultaneously, paradoxically cancel each other out, yet at the same time, awaken an unpredictable aspect of human potential. The world you knew has irrevocably changed, twisted beyond comprehension. Will you embrace the powers, or cling to the fading remains of your humanity? The choice is yours.

Genre:

Eldritch Apocalyptic scenario in modern world.

Status:

Completed (V2.5) Release Date: 13 January 2025

objects.title: The Deal
objects.text:
Synopsis:

Greetings, Worm! Your pitiful existence is so painfully mundane; it bores me beyond measure. Fear not, for I, a cosmic entity beyond your comprehension, am here to offer you a chance to transform your reality into something truly extraordinary. You are one of the fortunate few to be bestowed this opportunity, and let it be known that refusal is not an option. Embrace these deals and gain powers that mortals can only dream of. Of course, there's a small price to pay, but who expects quality products for free, right? Who me? I'm just a mere Benefactor of sorts..

Genre:

Classic Power Picker with some hidden lore.

Status:

Completed (V2) Release Date: 27 January 2025

objects.title: Project E.S.P.E.R
objects.text:
Synopsis:

Greetings, Worm! An alien corpse fell from the stars. Burnt, broken, and very much dead, Yet even in death, Its DNA still pulsed with power beyond anything our understanding. Power not meant for us… but power we could steal. So, of course, humanity did what it does best. We turned it into a weapon... Thus began Project E.S.P.E.R. You, Subject [REDACTED], are one of the rare few whose biology can host its fractured genome. You weren’t asked to join.. we just kidnapped you

Genre:

Secret Esper governmental projects set in IRL world.

Status:

WIP (V1) Release Date: 10 July 2025

objects.text: While I normally do original works, I am willing to do CYOA related to any existing fandom, but in case I'm totally new to the franchise, I will be dependent on your input.
I will strictly be doing SFW Works, I'm just not comfortable working with NSFW content.
Base rates will start from $100, But depending on length, complexity, Time invested, They will go up. For Reference: The Deal =$120, Marked One =$150 & Ruined Reality =$240
After discussing details regarding your CYOA and finalizing on an approach, You're requested to send an upfront payment in advance.
Time to complete your commission varies greatly, It can be finished within 2-3 months or may take an additional month, It depends on how busy I would be.
I have power to reject any requests, whether it being due to theme, time management or anything else.
I will still be making Original CYOAs, Commissions are just my attempts to help support my family and all.
CYOAs commissioned will be released like normal, Unless you have some genuine reason for not doing that.

I'm confident enough in my skills to take any commission requests.

rows.title: Wanna Help out?
rows.titleText:
My works are and will always be free to play, as I believe in making them accessible to everyone.
However, creating CYOAs requires a significant amount of time, effort, and dedication. If you enjoy my creations and would like to support me in continuing to make more, your tips or donations would be deeply appreciated.
<b>Every little bit helps!<b>

defaultRowText: This is a row, and inside of it, you can place choices. On both rows and choices Requirements can be placed, which will block a row from being viewed, or make the player unable to select a choice, depending on either Point-types or the Ids of other choices. Point-types can be made in Features then Manage Points. Hovering over buttons will explain what they do. The Design of the project can be changed in 'Modify Design' at the side navigation bar, and private styling for each row can be turned on in the rows Settings. Default text like this can be turned off in Features -> Manage Defaults.
defaultChoiceText: This is a Choice, and inside of it, you can place images and text. Scores can be added to it, and have Point-types attached. Addons can be added underneath the image and text. In the Functions at the bottom of the choice, there is an array of different things that can be done. Default text like this can be turned off in Features then Manage Defaults.
